title: Liberty Latin America (LILAK) Shares Cross Above 200 DMA - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Wednesday, shares of Liberty Latin America Ltd (Symbol: LILAK) crossed above their 200 day moving average of $17.85, changing hands as high as $18.45 per share. Liberty Latin America Ltd shares are currently trading up about 5% on the day.
